Okoboji bụ obodo dị na obodo Dickinson Iowa Steeti jikọrọ ọnụ n'akụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ nke Ọdọ Mmiri West Okoboji na mpaghara Iowa nnukwu  ọdọ mmiri N'oge ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ nke afọ 2020, ndị bi na ya bụ 768.
Dị ka United States Census Bureau si kwuo, obodo ahụ nwere ngụkọta mpaghara nke 1.86 square miles (4.82 km2), nke 1.85 square miles (4.79 km2) bụ ala na 0.01 square miles (0.03 km2) bụ mmiri.

Okoboji Community School District na-eje ozi ọtụtụ n'ime obodo ahụ. E guzobere mpaghara ahụ na July 1, 1988 site na njikọta nke Arnolds Park na Milford school districts. Okoboji High School dị na Milford bụ ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị dị n'ógbè ahụ.
Okoboji bụ nnukwu ebe njem nleta n'oge ọkọchị

Ọnụ ọgụgụ na-arịwanye elu nke ebe ezumike gburugburu Iowa Great Lakes na nso nso nke ebe ndị njem nleta ndị ọzọ, dị ka Arnolds Park na Spirit Lake, enyela aka na ewu ewu ya.  Okoboji aghọwokwa aha a ma ama na mba ahụ n'ihi ahịa nke ọtụtụ ngwaahịa ndị na-eji mpako na-egosipụta aha obodo ahụ na mkpụrụedemede siri ike

Ndị nleta na Okoboji ga-ahụ ozugbo mkpado bumper, iko, na sweatshirts na-eto Mahadum Okoboji nke efu ebe ọtụtụ ndị obodo na-azọrọ na ha nwetara agụmakwụkwọ. T-shirts ma ọ bụ sweatshirts nke Mahadum Okoboji na-ewu ewu n'etiti ụmụ akwụkwọ kọleji na Midwest.
